text: Mukhammedkalyi Abylgaziev (, ; born 20 January 1968) is a Kyrgyz politician. He was the Prime Minister of Kyrgyzstan from 20 April 2018 to 17 June 2020.Kyrgyz Parliament Approves New Prime Minister, Cabinet ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Kyrgyzstan
